You’re going to have one kid! You’ll teach them how to read, how to write, and how to perfectly arrange everything in the refrigerator. Congrats!
Getty You got: You will have twins! You’re going to have two babies at once! That’s even more exciting than a perfectly organized closet. How thrilling!
You got: You will have three kiddos! You’re going to have a trio of children! Maybe two of them will be twins! Only time will tell. Congratulations!
You got: You will have four kids! Holy moly! You’re going to have four kids. Don’t worry. You’re going to be a great parent! We know it. Congrats!
You got: You will have six kids! Wowza! You’re going to fill your home with six lil’ sprouts. Thats a lot of people! It’ll be hard work but it’s worth it. Congrats!
You got: You’re seriously just going to have a lots of dogs! Congrats! You’re going to fill your home with adorable pups. You’re just too busy right now for kids right now so you’ll get lots of doggos and spoil them! Boop!
